4. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper mentions using images as content to generate recommendations, which is a topic within computer vision. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel approach to personalized ranking, which is a topic within artificial intelligence.
